**What I decided goes on the Home page:**

The Home page should answer *"What do I need right now, and can I get there fast?"* — three rings:

1. **At-a-glance status** (sessions, cron pressure, system health)
2. **Quick access** (one-click routes — currently absent, biggest gap)
