- FLOATING aesthetic (warm cream/ivory, forest green, glass-card depth, editorial hierarchy)
- 3-zone layout: Hero → Quick-access grid → 2-col Pulse/Intel → 2-col Secondary
- Restraint over decoration; every widget answers a real question
- Micro-interactions: hover lift on tiles, ambient pulse on status dot

